data.name: XTreeControl
desc: An interface to a control that displays a set of hierarchical data as an outline.

properties.name: DefaultCollapsedGraphicURL
desc: If the given URL points to a loadable graphic, the graphic is rendered before collapsed non leaf nodes.
This can be overridden for individual nodes by XTreeNode.getCollapsedGraphicURL()

properties.name: DefaultExpandedGraphicURL
desc: If the given URL points to a loadable graphic, the graphic is rendered before expanded non leaf nodes.
This can be overridden for individual nodes by XTreeNode.getExpandedGraphicURL()
